          "description": "Dr Rawdin is an exceptional prosthodontist. His colleagues and staff are professional, empathetic and knowledgeable. As a dental phobic, I hadn\u2019t treated for way too long with expected deterioration. Dr Rawdin and his Daughter, Dr Sam, did a tremendous job in restoring my smile in a painless and relaxing environment. I actually look forward to periodic visits to maintain great dental health. Fantastic practice! Top notch!",
