          "description": "My family has been going to Gallery57 for 10+ years now. They are so caring, provide excellent services, and have state of the art facilities. The staff are extremely professional, notably the hygienists (Elena, Rosie and Aliza) are so thorough and so kind. The dentists- we see Dr Koenigsberg and Dr Rebecca  --are  simply best in their field and we trust them with all our dental needs. They (father and daughter duo!) have both been there for us through several dental crises! We love this practice.",
