          "description": "Went today for the first time for cleaning. From the moment you walk in, everyone at the front desk was really nice and welcoming. I saw Luz for cleaning and she was thorough and the whole process was quick and painless free. Left the office w no pain afterwards as i usually am after a cleaning appointment. Dr. Samantha Rawdin came in after my visit and was great. Amazing table side manners and patient answering all my questions where she made it easy for me to understand. Thank you again for a great first visit. Look forward to seeing you again in 6 months.",
