          "description": "I can\u2019t say enough superlatives about this practice. Dr. K and Dr. Rebecca are OUTSTANDING. In terms of dentistry, they are SUPERB - as well as being genuinely caring and kind.  They are conservative -only recommending what they feel is necessary or when not intervening could cause worse future problems.Refreshing  to have such high-end practitioners with the attitude that sometimes the most effective strategy is to do less not more! On site state of the art lab so you are generally spared the misery of multiple visits if you need a crown - one visit and the entire process is done! The entire staff is wonderful. I actually look forward to seeing Oscar every four or five months he\nis very thorough but makes the cleaning painless and is such a terrific guy. Highest recommendation! Thank you all so much.",
