          "description": "Dr. Orlando is an exceptional dentist, and anyone looking for someone they can truly trust with their oral health should see him. Even though he is out of network, the quality of care he provides makes it more than worth it. After having a terrible experience with a previous dentist who caused more harm than good, finding Dr. Orlando was a breath of fresh air. Everyone in the office is also very friendly, communicative and thorough. The office is also beautiful.\n\nHe is knowledgeable, thorough, and genuinely cares about his patients. Most recently, he made a spot-on diagnosis based on the my symptoms and immediately referred me to an endodontist\u2014ultimately saving a tooth and preventing future pain. His attentiveness and clinical judgment made a real difference.\n\nGrateful doesn\u2019t even begin to cover it. It\u2019s rare to find a dentist you feel completely safe with, and Dr. Orlando is exactly that. Highly recommended.",
